snippet.title: GeneRally 2 - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
GeneRally 2 is a top-down arcade racing game with a built-in track editor coming to Steam Early Access on the 30th of May 2023!

It's currently available to wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2104920/GeneRally_2/

Music Composed by Olli Oja.

GeneRally 2 on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2104920/GeneRally_2/
GeneRally 2 Website - https://gene-rally2.com
GeneRally on Twitter - https://www.twitter.com/Gene_Rally
GeneRally on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/GeneRallyGame
